3. Notable Incidents: PromptLock AI ransomware (2026); Cisco attack (2025); Google zero-days; Microsoft patches; cloud outages (AWS/Azure/Cloudflare).
4. Predictions: Targeted ransomware, AI fragmentation, infrastructure attacks, event-tied hacktivism; $520B annual spending.
